<tableCitation box="[1213,1341,1196,1220]" captionStart-0="TABLE 1" captionStart-1="TABLE 2" captionStartId-0="4.[125,211,518,541]" captionStartId-1="10.[151,239,1159,1183]" captionTargetBox-0="[139,1873,697,1546]" captionTargetBox-1="[160,1422,1248,1945]" captionTargetPageId-0="4" captionTargetPageId-1="10" captionText-0="TABLE 1. List of species of Polycirrus used for comparison with the species described in this paper, with the main morphological characters used for the identification. Taxa already recorded for Brazilian waters are marked with a “ * ”; (-) unknown or not observed. Sources: Kinberg (1866); Hessle (1917); Hutchings and Murray (1984); Hutching and Glasby (1986); Hutchings (1993); Glasby and Glasby (2006); characters of Polycirrus abrolhensis, P. bicrinalis, P. glaucus, P. paivai, and P. variabilis examined on type-material." captionText-1="TABLE 2. Comparison between the species of Polycirrus described in this paper, with the main morphological characters used in the identification. (-) unknown or not observed." httpUri-0="http://table.plazi.org/id/99D0ADDADD3CFF804142D34BFE238552" httpUri-1="http://table.plazi.org/id/99D0ADDADD32FF8E41A8D5CAFCE1839A" pageId="3" pageNumber="149" tableUuid-0="99D0ADDADD3CFF804142D34BFE238552" tableUuid-1="99D0ADDADD32FF8E41A8D5CAFCE1839A">
